        "text": "STANDARD FORM NO. 64\nOffice Memorandum • UNITED STATES GOVERNMENT\nTO : Director, FBI\nDATE: April 21, 1959\nFROM : SAC, Birmingham (62-0)\nSUBJECT: AERIAL PHENOMENA RESEARCH GROUP\nMISCELLANEOUS"
